### 2. Database Schema

#### [NEW] `supabase/schema.sql`
Complete SQL with all tables, indexes, RLS policies, triggers, and seed data:
- `users` (extends `auth.users`)
- `rooms` (with `amenities jsonb`, `gallery jsonb`)
- `bookings` (with status enums)
- `seasonal_pricing`
- `reviews`
- `blog_posts`
- `add_on_services`
- `booking_addons` (junction)
- `coupons`

RLS: Guests can read rooms/availability, create/view own bookings. Admins can read/write all.

---

### 3. Middleware & Auth

#### [NEW] `middleware.ts`
- Protect `/dashboard`, `/admin` routes
- Redirect unauthenticated users to `/auth/login`
- Inject Supabase session into server context

#### [NEW] `src/app/auth/login/page.tsx` + `register/page.tsx`
- Email/password auth via Supabase
- Google OAuth option
- Elegant full-screen forms with tropical imagery

#### [NEW] `src/app/auth/callback/route.ts`
OAuth callback handler.

---

### 4. API Routes

#### [NEW] `src/app/api/rooms/route.ts`
GET: List active rooms with optional filters (category, guests, price).

#### [NEW] `src/app/api/rooms/[slug]/route.ts`
GET: Single room detail with pricing.

#### [NEW] `src/app/api/availability/route.ts`
GET: Blocked dates for a room (booked + seasonal closures).
POST: Validate date range availability before booking.

#### [NEW] `src/app/api/bookings/route.ts`
POST: Create booking — validates availability, calculates seasonal price, creates pending booking.

#### [NEW] `src/app/api/bookings/[id]/route.ts`
GET: Booking detail (auth-required, own booking or admin).
PATCH: Update booking status (admin only).
DELETE: Cancel booking (guest — within policy window).

#### [NEW] `src/app/api/pricing/route.ts`
GET: Calculate price for date range (seasonal multiplier applied).

#### [NEW] `src/app/api/reviews/route.ts`
GET: Reviews for a room. POST: Submit review (auth required, must have completed booking).

#### [NEW] `src/app/api/blog/route.ts` + `[slug]/route.ts`
Blog CRUD.

#### [NEW] `src/app/api/payments/stripe/route.ts`
Create Stripe PaymentIntent (partial 30% or full).

#### [NEW] `src/app/api/payments/webhook/route.ts`
Stripe webhook — confirm payment, update booking status, trigger email.

#### [NEW] `src/app/api/email/route.ts`
Send confirmation email via Resend.

#### [NEW] `src/app/api/og/route.tsx`
Dynamic OG image generation with `@vercel/og`.

---

### 5. Shared Components (Atomic Design)

#### Atoms
- `Button` — variants: primary/secondary/ghost, sizes, loading state
- `Badge` — category, status, price
- `Input`, `Textarea`, `Select` — form primitives
- `StarRating` — display-only and interactive
- `CurrencyDisplay` — LKR/USD/EUR switcher
- `Spinner`, `Skeleton` — loading states

#### Molecules
- `RoomCard` — image, title, price, rating, max guests, hover elevation
- `ReviewCard` — avatar, rating, comment, date
- `BlogCard` — cover, title, excerpt, category
- `BookingWidget` — check-in/out date pickers + guests + Book Now CTA
- `PriceCalculator` — shows base + seasonal + taxes
- `AddOnCard` — service name, price, toggle
- `GalleryThumb` — thumbnail with lightbox trigger

#### Organisms
- `Navbar` — transparent → sticky with blur on scroll, mobile drawer
- `HeroSection` — full-screen, video/image, gradient overlay, booking widget
- `AmenitiesGrid` — icon + label grid (WiFi, AC, pool, pickup etc.)
- `RoomGrid` — filterable grid
- `AvailabilityCalendar` — react-day-picker, blocked dates highlighted
- `ImageGallery` — Swiper slider + lightbox
- `ReviewsSection` — rating summary + card list
- `AddOnSelector` — multi-select with price summary
- `CheckoutForm` — guest details + payment selector
- `AdminSidebar` + `AdminStats` cards
- `Footer` — links, trust badges, social, WhatsApp CTA
- `ChatbotWidget` — floating AI chat bubble
- `WhatsAppButton` — fixed bottom-right float

