### 7. Booking Logic

#### [NEW] `src/lib/booking.ts`
```ts
// Check availability (no double booking via DB unique constraint)
checkAvailability(roomId, checkIn, checkOut): Promise<boolean>

// Calculate price with seasonal multipliers
calculatePrice(roomId, checkIn, checkOut, currency): Promise<PriceBreakdown>

// Apply coupon
applyCoupon(code, subtotal): Promise<DiscountResult>

// Create booking (atomic transaction)
createBooking(payload: BookingPayload): Promise<Booking>

// Minimum stay enforcement
validateMinimumStay(checkIn, checkOut, minNights): boolean
```

---

### 8. SEO & Metadata

#### [NEW] `src/app/layout.tsx`
Root metadata with Hotel schema, viewport, theme-color.

Each page exports `generateMetadata()` using Next.js Metadata API with:
- `title`, `description`, `openGraph`, `twitter`
- `alternates.canonical`
- JSON-LD `Hotel` / `BlogPosting` schemas via `<script>` tag

