## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
No existing test suite. I will verify at the file level:
```bash
# TypeScript compilation check
npx tsc --noEmit

# Dev server starts without errors
npm run dev
```

### Browser Verification (via browser subagent)
1. Navigate to `http://localhost:3000` — verify hero renders, booking widget visible
2. Navigate to `/rooms` — verify room cards load
3. Navigate to `/blog` — verify blog posts render
4. Navigate to `/contact` — verify form and WhatsApp button
5. Navigate to `/admin` — verify redirect to login (auth guard)
6. Navigate to `/auth/login` — verify login form renders

### Manual Verification Points
- Tailwind styles applied correctly (tropical palette)
- Navbar becomes sticky + opaque on scroll
- Mobile responsive at 375px viewport
- Room card hover animation works
